=== SECURITY_TERMINAL ===
# id: 91
# title: The Security Terminal
# chinese_title: 安保终端
# category: Terminal
# mode: dungeon

A security monitoring station still receives feeds from scattered cameras throughout the station. Most show empty corridors, but some reveal movement — scavengers, creatures, and something else that the cameras can't quite focus on. The system also controls door locks.

* [Unlock doors to restricted areas]
  ~ gain_radical("门")
  "锁" (suǒ) — lock, to lock. Related to "门" (mén) — door.
* [Monitor the camera feeds for threats]
  ~ gain_xp(20)
  "视" (shì) — to watch, vision
* [Download the security logs]
  ~ gain_gold(15)
  "安" (ān) — safety, security
* [Lock doors behind you for protection]
  ~ heal(5)
  "关" (guān) — to close, to lock
